  <h2>What To Do If You've Spotted Any of These Signs</h2>

  <p><strong>Book a sweep before you use the fire again.</strong> This isn't a job for a spray can and a YouTube video — a professional sweep has the brushes, rods and experience to do it properly and tell you honestly what they found.</p>

  <p>In Melbourne, the busy period is May and June — right when everyone suddenly remembers their chimney as the cold arrives. Book in autumn and you'll get a time that suits you rather than waiting with a fireplace you can't use.</p>

